						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/Video-lessons-learned-from-the-Dutch-Biodiversity-Fund" title="Video-lessons learned from the Dutch Biodiversity Fund " alt="link">Video-lessons learned from the Dutch Biodiversity Fund </a></h2>

	
					<p>








 




  
  

	
	<a href="/var/knowledge/storage/images/media/images/hivos/299069-1-eng-GB/Hivos.gif" rel="lightbox[]">	
	  </a>
	
		
			
	
  	






	 
  





	Hivos-Oxfam Novib produced two videos containing lessons learnt and experiences with biodiverse agricultural systems. The first DVD focuses on biodiversity strategic value: conserving production processes and the second on biodiversity Strategic value: farmer knowledge and livelihood strategies. (Source: HIVOS, 15 April 2010)</p>
							<p><span class="date">26/04/2010</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/Video-lessons-learned-from-the-Dutch-Biodiversity-Fund">Read more...</a>
